{"id":181866,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":3,"day":30}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"347","ytitle":"","mtitle":"垦荒","ftitle":"","authors":["谷雨"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噹啷啷………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上爆着大颗的汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长把锣儿敲得遍村响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发动全村的嫂子、庄稼汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挤满在打麦场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩着锄和铲；篓和筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么轻松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么紧张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着啊!加紧生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着啊!努力垦荒!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞着锣锤，背了篓筐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从平地到高岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥大伙儿从这边垦到那响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百把锄头，铁铲，臂膀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结合了有说，有笑，有唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们唱——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“山上的荒地是什么人来开………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们唱——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们的任务是大伙儿垦荒……”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄的锄，担的担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的太阳转向西方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有倦意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有颓丧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有说，有笑，有唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片长满荆棘的荒场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它已变了样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那么整齐的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一畦畦，一行行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就得加紧播种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取收获渡春荒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克服国家的大困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠咱们尽力量”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长把话刚说完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙儿紧接着欢嚷——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“响应号召加紧生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有的是力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待开好这一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再垦那一方”。"}]}